{
  "texts": [
    "This gave me a different kind of comfort by glimpsing another mode of familial relationships.",
    "\"In a few cases, we found participants spent much more effort on describing themselves than describing the chatbot (P4, P14).",
    "For instance, P4 once simply created a chatbot to play \"a friend\" without further information, but elaborated on their situations with an extensive and heartfelt text: \"I am getting to start my Ph.D. study soon and need to read papers every day, which is quite boring.",
    "Also, I felt staying alone always makes me want to talk to someone.",
    "I am a highly sensitive person and care so much about every single sentence others say, and tend to over-interpret what they mean."
  ]
}